Uses of Package
org.jcvi.jillion.assembly

  • Packages that use org.jcvi.jillion.assembly 
    Package Description
    org.jcvi.jillion.assembly
    The assembly package contains objects for working with genomic data that has been assembled into Contigs and Scaffolds.
    org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.ca.asm
    Contains Classes and interfaces to work with Celera Assembler data.
    org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.clc.cas.read  
    org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.clc.cas.transform  
    org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed
    This package contains classes for working with Consed.
    org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed.ace
    This package contains classes for handling Contigs stored in the Ace File Format.
    org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed.nav  
    org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed.transform  
    org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.tigr.contig
    This package contains classes that can read and write TIGR .contig formatted contig data (also known as .ctg format).
    org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.tigr.tasm
    This package contains classes to handle TIGR Assembler formatted assembly files.
    org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.util
    The Assembly util package contains utility classes that are useful for working with general assembly data regardless of what assembler was used or file format the data is in.
    org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.util.consensus
    The Consensus package will compute Consensus for a given Slice.
    org.jcvi.jillion.experimental.assembly.agp  
    org.jcvi.jillion.experimental.ncbi.submit.assemblyArchive  
    org.jcvi.jillion.internal.assembly  
    org.jcvi.jillion.internal.assembly.util  
    org.jcvi.jillion.sam.transform
    This package transforms SAM encoded files into other assembly "contexts" using AssemblyTransformer.
  • Classes in org.jcvi.jillion.assembly used by org.jcvi.jillion.assembly 
    Class and Description
    AbstractContigBuilder
    AbstractContigBuilder implements the ContigBuilder interface
    AssembledRead
    A AssembledRead is a read that has been assembled and placed at a particular location in its assembly.
    AssembledReadBuilder
    Builds an AssembledRead for a specific contig.
    AssemblyTransformationService
    AssemblyTransformationService is an interface that will parse some kind of Assembly data into messages that an AssemblyTransformer can use.
    AssemblyTransformer
    AssemblyTransformer is an interface to transform one assembly format into another.
    Contig
    A Contig is a CONTIGuous region of genomic data.
    ContigBuilder
    ContigBuilder is a Builder for Contigs that allows creating a contig object by adding placed reads and setting a consensus.
    ContigDataStore
    ContigDataStore is a marker interface for a DataStore implementation which stores Contigs of the same type.
    ContigDataStoreTransfomationService 
    ContigDataStoreTransfomationService.Builder 
    GappedReferenceBuilder
    GappedReferenceBuilder builds a GAPPED reference NucleotideSequence from an initial ungapped reference sequence and lots of insertions to various offsets made by aligned reads.
    PlacedContig 
    ReadInfo
    ReadInfo is a value object that contains a read's trim information.
    Scaffold
    A scaffold (also known as a super-contig) is a layout of Contigs placed and oriented together such that it can be determined the distance and orientation between contigs.
    ScaffoldBuilder
    ScaffoldBuilder is a Builder that builds a single Scaffold.
    ScaffoldDataStoreBuilder
